Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.51,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HBB7CEF&\3c&HEBE1EA&}少年少女的\N{\fs65\c&HF2F2F2&\3c&H9C59DC&}恋爱圣经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像是刚才校长从学生那里没收的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.98,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\pos(350,888)\bord4}白银御行还没做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:10.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他说「这书对学生的影响不好所以你们处理掉」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 他就不能自己处理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对学生影响不好的书？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:19.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是淫乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:23.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家变得淫乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:26.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗 那么慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是有未和谐x毛的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:31.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银产生了浓厚的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.01,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜 还是不要打开比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:32.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:35.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,关于「第一次是在什么时候」的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「在高中的时候」占34%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是骗人的 怎么可能有那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,34% 也就是说占三分之一以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:50.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是一个班30人 那么有10个人已经做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:54.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在这3人当中 有1人已初体验过的可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:56.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为读这种书的人做的调查问卷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:00.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以结果才这么高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你是说「样本选择偏差」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上的确不会有像结果所说的那么多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:06.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:08.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒觉得这个比例是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说反而觉得太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 该不会说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:22.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜同学你…已经体验过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 在很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:31.60,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60\b1\bord5\3c&H4FB677&\c&H3D50CB&}黄{\c&HDADCDC&}页
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:31.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 青森的市外局编号是017啊 真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说上了高中都该经历过了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:38.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,二位还真是在缺乏爱的环境中成长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:44.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我也赶紧找个男朋友比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:44.93,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,长万部的市外局编号是01377 啊 013
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:48.19,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,不过爸爸他肯定不会允许的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:50.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜觉察到二人有些焦虑的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人们总是与周围相比较
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,发现自己落后于人时就会感到焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:04:00.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这份焦虑就会让尽快找伴侣的心情进一步萌发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的体验落后于人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.93,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs65\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1328,712)}我\N落\N后\N于\N人\N了\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.93,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs65\c&HFFFFFF&\frz270\pos(1298,790)}……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.93,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs65\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1344,926)}？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.93,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs65\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1054,848)}要\N赶\N紧\N找\N个\N女\N朋\N友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.93,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs65\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1066,918)}！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.93,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs65\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(770,790)}四\N宫\N和\N我\N交\N往\N吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.93,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs65\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(780,862)}！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫 和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,被告白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜定下了今天的行动方针
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么愚蠢的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:25.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀会长 听说您很受人欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:26.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煽动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您没有女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煽风点火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有和特定的对象建立那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:38.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「现在」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好像给人感觉是过去有过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:43.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算至今没有与人交往过也不算是说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常方便的一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是不分老少 被全世界所爱用的一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:52.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 白银御行并没有恋爱经验
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:56.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但白银他却并不是不受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要说的话 他还是挺受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过 该说是物以类聚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:06.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说有了怪人容易和怪人结缘的现实所致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他容易吸引一些危险人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.91,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\b1\c&H6857E2&\frz356.9\pos(1172.8,460.8)\fad(450,0)}这\N是\N什\N么\N毛\N!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:13.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以迄今为止从未成功交往过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.25,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\b1\c&H6857E2&\fad(230,0)\frz9.772\pos(606.4,273.6)}这\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.25,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\b1\c&H6857E2&\fad(230,0)\frz9.772\pos(572.8,456)}什\N么\N烟\N!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:19.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会这么受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,故而白银虽然没有恋爱经验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:26.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,却获得了「我很受欢迎」这一强烈自信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:31.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是我充满知性的一面让女性为之沦陷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多么地充满罪恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:38.51,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,现——在——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:38.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这个男人正是同时拥有无比自信与纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,现代社会所孕育的异类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:41.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是怪物处男
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 那您一定是有经验的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.90,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,然而这只怪物也有他的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:54.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是处男这一事实…无法改变！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎是很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对体验过的人说自己体验过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:04.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是外行人想要骗电影爱好者说自己很懂电影一样的无谋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:07.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我撒了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是很有经验的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,打肿脸充胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:14.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您就对暴露自己纯洁的经历这么害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:21.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛…我想做就能做到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到的只有逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长您有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为您和妹妹经常做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,…才不会做啊 你蠢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可你们是家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我和刚出生的侄子就做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还用摄像机录下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,过度害怕与人接触可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是现代社会的黑暗之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:01.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是贵族阶级的黑暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同学不也经常和佩斯做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:09.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊 不要把我卷进去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:13.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫家的教育方针竟然异常至此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:18.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,将这种事当作常识 已经不是不知世事的级别了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:19.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我姑且问一下你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道「第一次」指的是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,请别把我当傻瓜行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,作为淑女 我至少还是知道这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是指「亲吻」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:43.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫辉夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,作为财团大小姐的16年间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:51.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,自小就生活在限制性知识的环境中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:55.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对她来说 性知识的极限就停留在亲吻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.75,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H789B54&\fs60\pos(985,153)}性的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.75,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H789B54&\fs60\pos(1030,236)}雌蕊 雄蕊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.75,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H789B54&\fs60\pos(1075,309)}结婚之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.75,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H789B54&\fs60\pos(1220,390)}就一切交给男方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.75,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H789B54&\fs60\pos(1176,467)}完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在那以上的事就相当于都市传说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这方面的事就与我无关了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:06.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说是超级「深闺大小姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然她也不可能知道「第一次」的真正含义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 下面让我来说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:24.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所说的「第一次」是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:26.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:31.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,…的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:34.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:37.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,像是野兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:52.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说那种事法律规定要结婚后才行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 还以为心脏要停了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫败北
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:12.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银同学 我不喜欢与人接触
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:14.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我一个人呆着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:35.80,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord4\pos(428,930)}辉夜大小姐想被猜中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是安静的夜晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:35.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原书记说是今天负责带佩斯散步就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,佩斯 佩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:46.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上会计不知不觉地跑来又不知不觉地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:51.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人虽然不起眼但是全勤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:10:00.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和过去比起来变得更圆滑了啊 四宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是说我胖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是生活层面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么老套的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,确实啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:14.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也努力过让自己更加讨人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:21.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 我也渐渐开始了解你的为人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:25.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了解我为人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:31.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一起在学生会工作已经半年了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该算是对你有一定了解了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来测试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:38.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,测试？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:44.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 试试看会长究竟了解我到哪一步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:48.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说过「20个问题」的游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「20个问题」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:55.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,提问者要在20个问题内猜测出出题者心里所想的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:11:00.30,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H313033&\fs80\1a&H31&\pos(1658,778)}是\N手\N掌\N的\N大\N小\N？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:11:00.30,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H313033&\fs80\1a&H31&\pos(614,436)}能\N吃\N吗\N？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:11:00.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是提问仅限于能回答YES或NO的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.30,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在所想的是橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:03.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在20个问题之内猜出就是提问者胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,反之则出题者胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:12.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 如果提出20个问题一般都能猜出大致答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:15.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你既然说了解我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:18.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那即使砍半 只提10个问题也应该能回答出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:19.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:26.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.46,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H171621&\3c&HFFFDFF&\fs110\bord5\an7\pos(108,338)\fad(180,500)}※能装20发的比利时手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.46,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H171621&\3c&HFFFDFF&\fs110\bord5\an7\pos(154,450)\fad(180,500)}”Henrion Dassy&Heuschen”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.46,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H171621&\3c&HFFFDFF&\fs110\bord5\an7\pos(184,558)\fad(180,500)}（子弹只装了10发）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我的第一个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一 那是能摸到的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:41.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,YES 并不是言语或概念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,二 那是电器产品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:44.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:48.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,三 那是温暖或冰冷的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,由刚才的回答能推出的结论有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:57.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,生物 食物 或是像热水及冰那样的物质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又亦或是营火或能调节温度的器具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:01.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:06.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在有多了解四宫这个测试的前提下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:09.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,答案一定是与四宫辉夜有关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四 它是四宫的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,五 是四宫今天触碰过的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:21.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:24.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,六 四宫家有这个东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,连续三个NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:32.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,本来以为是四宫的某样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,现在完全没有头绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再从四宫的心理找找线索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:38.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,七 是四宫喜欢的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？这个表情是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:56.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点害羞 难为情的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:58.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:05.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,八 那是生物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微冷静点 再确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以摸得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是电子产品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是常温的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是四宫的所有物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有碰过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也不在四宫家里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,符合条件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一个 是四宫喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,委婉的告白！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:41.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:45.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,九 是哪种喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友之间的 还是作为一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是其他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:57.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有答案 因为没办法用YES或NO回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:58.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太着急 浪费子弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:01.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:04.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还有可能是其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 十
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:15.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常聪明 帅气 头发的颜色有点鲜艳 眸若清泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:32.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 绝对是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这么别扭的爱的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:42.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来 真是发生了很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:46.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 每次都对四宫有新认识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:51.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:59.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 问题都问完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:08.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在某种程度上我很了解四宫这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:11.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫每次这样的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:12.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:16.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,准确的说应该是藤原书记养的佩斯
